modules.description: This module computes differences between two arrays of items, producing a list of change blocks indicating deletions, additions, or equal segments. It works directly with arrays of a custom item type and structures the output using `diff` and `t` types to represent the changes. Concrete use cases include comparing lines of text or sequences of tokens to visualize modifications between versions.
